ed in combination with antipsychotics or other antidopaminergic agents (e.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/32867/', '', 'Dexfenfluramine, Naltrexone, Ephedrine, Phentermine, Orlistat, Diethylpropion, Mazindol', 'Amisulpride, Lumateperone, Cariprazine, Pimavanserin', 1767369485);
